dothis
===

What's this?
---

This script is a command line utility which executes given command.
When the command is done (or interrupted), a growl notification will raise.

Example
---

  $ dothis.pl echo hello world
  hello world  # Growl notification will appear on your screen

  $ dothis.pl sleep 3
  # ditto, but 3 seconds later

  $ dothis.pl sleep 3
  ^C  # A notification titled "Interrupted" will appear

